B.ae1=new A.aa(B.EN,["Connect Booking.com","Connect Airbnb","Configure iCal",u.w,"Connect your Airbnb listing so Cabinly can read your availability and keep calendars in sync. This helps prevent double bookings and gives you a complete view of what's already booked.","Add your iCal URL to sync availability from platforms without direct integrations. This keeps your calendar up to date across all channels.","Your Booking.com listing URL","Your Airbnb listing URL","Your iCal URL","e.g. booking.com/hotel/pl/twoj-drugi-dom-na-kaszubach.pl.html","e.g. airbnb.com/rooms/123456","e.g. https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/..."],t.w)
